Html: In the Frost tree, I don't see any of the changes, including Improved Icy Talons and Endless Winter.  Is it a graphical error or should my dps actually be higher since Rawr isn't adding the 4% strength from Endless Winter?

To verify that talents are affecting the character, go to the Comparisons Chart selector and choose Talents. From there you can find the talent by name to see it's present value (either next rank or last rank, depending on how many ranks you have in it already). If the value is 0 at all ranks then it's either not modelled or it's conflicting with an Active Buff of the same name. So turn the buff off if that's the case.
